			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 0,
				"to": 7340
			},
			"text": " The Florida Everglades stretch across millions of acres of slow moving water and dense sawgrass."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:07,340",
				"to": "00:00:10,960"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 7340,
				"to": 10960
			},
			"text": " It is one of the most specialized ecosystems on Earth."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:10,960",
				"to": "00:00:16,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 10960,
				"to": 16200
			},
			"text": " But right now, a massive predator is moving just beneath the surface."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:16,200",
				"to": "00:00:18,760"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 16200,
				"to": 18760
			},
			"text": " And it was never supposed to be here."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:18,760",
				"to": "00:00:26,220"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 18760,
				"to": 26220
			},
			"text": " In the 1980s, Miami established itself as the exotic pet capital of the United States,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:26,220",
				"to": "00:00:32,360"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 26220,
				"to": 32360
			},
			"text": " importing thousands of foreign reptiles through its ports every single year."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:32,360",
				"to": "00:00:40,660"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 32360,
				"to": 40660
			},
			"text": " Consumers purchased baby Burmese pythons with no understanding of their explosive growth rate."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:40,660",
				"to": "00:00:46,440"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 40660,
				"to": 46440
			},
			"text": " Within months, these snakes reached lengths that made them impossible to keep."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:46,440",
				"to": "00:00:49,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 46440,
				"to": 49200
			},
			"text": " When the pythons outgrew their enclosures,"
